CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 13, 1962, pg. 2 reads: "New City Official - Atty. J. Warren Watson (left), recently sworn in as an assistant city solicitor, receives instructions from Solicitor David W. Craig, the chief of the city's law department, where Attorney Watson now works. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Assistant city solicitor Atty. J. Warren Watson and Solicitor David W. Craig seated behind desk in office interior with barrister bookcases
